page.title: 04A DAY IN MY LIFE PART 3
page.content: When Superman ends I switch off the video and I put on Mary Poppins which is on another tape. Then I leave Laura to watch Mary Poppins and I go and get a biscuit for myself.Then I normally go outside afterwards. The house is opposite the garages. In one of them my bike is stored. I play on it when it is a very nice day. Then I would probably go to my friends house. My friend is called Rosalind. We normally go out in the garden and have lunch. Then after I have played with her I go home.My dad comes in at about 8o'clock that is when I have my bath and hair wash. My dad always comes with something for me so I have a lot of lovely things.Then at nine o'clock I go to bed.
